- 'Prophecies' refer to the predicted closing prices; 
- 'Stock's vital signs' include opening price, high price, low price, close price, volume, and other relevant market data; 
- 'Identities of those who have checked the oracles' refer to the user IDs, names, emails, roles, access times, access types, IP addresses, devices, and locations of users who accessed the data; 
- 'Ranked by their clairvoyance' means ordered by the accuracy of the predictions; 
- 'Most recent inspecting time' refers to the access time of the data.
